U.K. Mortgages Reach Highest Number Since 2008, Moneyfacts Says

-- B y   S i m o n   P a c k a r d
-- 
2011-09-21T14:26:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/u-k-mortgages-reach-highest-number-since-2008-moneyfacts-says.html
The number of residential mortgages
available in the U.K. climbed to 3,035, the highest since
February 2008, according to personal finance website
Moneyfacts.co.uk.  Mortgage lending has increased from a 1,209 low reached in
April 2009, the website said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simon Packard in London at 
 packard@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Ermakova at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net  